 times in 2 weeks</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/m2OFKie</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zwESCK8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A friend sent me this post of Tic Tac on Saturday from an area rescue. She knew I was looking for a senior pup. Tic Tac is an old lady who deserves so much more than humans have given her.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hrz5Sgn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Obviously I immediately went to get her. I'm not a monster. Here she is on her freedom ride. Her smile broke and healed my heart all at once.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BdiJneE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>In her new home adjusting (with Waffle House leftovers lol). The crate will go away as soon as she's fully comfortable here.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5pRzK8M.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>On a walk with her new brother.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Mfbag31.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The dumbest part of this was the reason she kept getting returned. Literally "She's a velcro dog, she just wants to follow you around and it's annoying."

Yes, how awful to have a dog who wants to be with you. People are trash. 

We are her forever home. She's 11 years old and may not have long left, but whatever she has left will be here, peaceful, and full of love. She's a good girl.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/m2OFKie</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Bunicus]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Maximus Iphonius</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ICEhMM4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NgOVgkv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ICEhMM4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ecjecj]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ha!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GSrwyfR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w7V7ZWQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GSrwyfR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[angelinesg7]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>They're evolving</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/a1bzECh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BCzlsR5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/a1bzECh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Bountyhunterfromhell]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Paul Rudd is an artist</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nD8s2Rg</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/N1svZrz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/nD8s2Rg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[anlyin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>And in the US ....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JtF6ele</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hjgfTe9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JtF6ele</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[angelinesg7]]></dc:creator></ite